tid":1118393,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">利迷口講獌狗就算唔放水都冇可能贏到<br />\n但其實內心不知幾期待曼聯真係搏到曼城失分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n就好似我明知曼聯冇可能贏到巴塞 <br />\n但都會有一絲希望 希望反cup巴黎既奇蹟再次發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都係真<br />\n作為利好想獌贏鏝<br />\n但事實上獌太廢根本冇可能"},{"pid":"e7b2fb808b7c6cb77223faddc81dedf830531050","tid":1118393,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e915021942effd68f2835bac251004c46e2c971c","tid":1118393,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"獌準備好踢歐霸未？"},{"pid":"c9497afa08baa2074eb50b6656972da7b41d6ebd","tid":1118393,"uid":19676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"留名等睇臨尾香<br />\n<br />\n歐聯輸比巴塞<br />\n英超等二"},{"pid":"f0ab4cc3fde4f84290ec49fc028c139a14edfbd6","tid":1118393,"uid":70239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"熱刺贏巴？瞓撚醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406797b49e4e6b1dd27409c3292e467720f99f12","tid":1118393,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:28:09.000Z","msg":"笑到噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09646a15cfddc93ca191ea7375ace9e9de124468","tid":1118393,"uid":249347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好文"},{"pid":"6306d817e237f64fe5cbc41aa5672bbe13fd04ba","tid":1118393,"uid":123243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04